  "text": "The effect of lignin on the thermal degradation of isotactic polypropylene was studied by Canetti et al. [CITATION_1] . An increase in the thermal degradation temperature of the blends was observed as a function of lignin content. Maldhure et al. [CITATION_2] examined the influence of lignin in different amount on the thermal degradation behavior of polypropylene/lignin blends in nonoxidative atmospheres [CITATION_3] .",
